h \u0627\u0644\u0627\u064a\u0645\u0627\u0646","link":"https:\/\/www.abuaminaelias.com\/dailyhadithonline\/category\/faith-iman\/"},"img":{"alt_text":"","src":"","width":0,"height":0},"classes":[]},{"id":20896,"url":"https:\/\/www.abuaminaelias.com\/dailyhadithonline\/2015\/09\/12\/death-during-hajj-umrah\/","url_meta":{"origin":32391,"position":2},"title":"Hadith on Hajj: Reward for those who die during pilgrimage","author":"Abu Amina Elias","date":"September 12, 2015","format":false,"excerpt":"Abu Huraira reported: The Messenger of Allah, peace and blessings be upon him, said, \u201cWhoever goes out for the Hajj pilgrimage and dies, the reward of Hajj will be written for him until the Day of Resurrection. Whoever goes out for the Umrah pilgrimage and dies, the reward of Umrah\u2026","rel":"","context":"In &quot;Righteousness \u0627\u0644\u0628\u0631&quot;","block_context":{"text":"Righteousness \u0627\u0644\u0628\u0631","link":"https:\/\/www.abuaminaelias.com\/dailyhadithonline\/category\/righteousness-al-birr\/"},"img":{"alt_text":"","src":"","width":0,"height":0},"classes":[]},{"id":12638,"url":"https:\/\/www.abuaminaelias.com\/dailyhadithonline\/2013\/03\/05\/grey-hairs-in-islam\/","url_meta":{"origin":32391,"position":3},"title":"Hadith on Elders: Gray hairs in Islam are a blessing","author":"Abu Amina Elias","date":"March 5, 2013","format":false,"excerpt":"'Amr ibn 'Abasah reported: The Messenger of Allah, peace and blessings be upon him, said, \u201cWhoever has grown a gray hair in the way of Allah, it will be a light for him on the Day of Resurrection.\u201d Source: Sunan al-Tirmidhi\u0304 1635 Grade: Sahih\u00a0(authentic) according to Al-Tirimdhi \u0639\u064e\u0646\u0652 \u0639\u064e\u0645\u0652\u0631\u0650\u0648 \u0628\u0652\u0646\u0650\u2026","rel":"","context":"In &quot;Faith \u0627\u0644\u0627\u064a\u0645\u0627\u0646&quot;","block_context":{"text":"Faith \u0627\u0644\u0627\u064a\u0645\u0627\u0646","link":"https:\/\/www.abuaminaelias.com\/dailyhadithonl